            "title": "保利置業上月合同銷售按年跌37.5% 首4個月則升9.15%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">保利置業(00119)公布，今年4月份實現合同銷售35億元(人民幣‧下同)，較去年同期減少37.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"保利置業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/00119-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"保利置業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/00119-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">保利置業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內合同銷售涉及樓面13.9萬平方米，均價每平方米2.49萬元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若將今年首4個月累積計算，該公司累計實現合同銷售179億元，按年升9.15%；涉及樓面66.2萬平方米，均價每平方米2.71萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14912147-%e4%bf%9d%e5%88%a9%e7%bd%ae%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e5%90%88%e5%90%8c%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e8%b7%8c37-5-%e9%a6%964%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e5%89%87%e5%8d%879-15",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20240604_FI_source-web_00119.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-08 12:11:04",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "內地A股早市先跌後揚 深股跑贏 寧德時代市值重越萬億",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中央昨天公布的一攬子穩市場金融政策，繼續推動股市氣氛，內地A股今早低開高走，即將來港IPO的寧德時代(300750.SZ)市值重越萬億。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開11點後，初段跌幅最多曾擴大至14點，低見3327點，但數分鐘後已掉頭轉升，早市後段最高衝上3359點，倒升17點；滬指中午收報3355點，升12點或0.38%，半日成交2101.91億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指重新跑贏，早市最低見10067點，僅跌36點，未幾率先倒升，早市後段最高報10222點，漲118點；深指中午收報10207點，仍升103點或1.03%，成交4993.99億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也升28點或0.75%，收報3860點；創業板指數升34點或1.74%，報2031點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230629_FI_A股_9_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230629_FI_A股_9_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深市重磅股寧德時代來港IPO計畫已於日前通過上市聆訊，市傳投資者初步反應理想，或能以較A股折讓少於10%作價發H股。該股今早先回後揚升，最高曾見248.68元，升4.22%；中午收報247.87元，仍漲3.88%，市值膨脹至1.09萬億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另一邊廂，美國商務部發言人表示，白宮計劃撤銷前總統拜登時期提出的先進人工智能(AI)晶片出口限制政策。內地上市芯片股受壓，AI芯片股寒武紀(688256.SH)逆市跌1.81%，報708.01元。中芯國際(00981)A股(688981.SH)在派季度成績表前，股價亦跌0.83%，報89.75元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14912029-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e5%85%88%e8%b7%8c%e5%be%8c%e6%8f%9a-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%91%e8%b4%8f-%e5%af%a7%e5%be%b7%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3%e5%b8%82%e5%80%bc%e9%87%8d%e8%b6%8a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-ap_China-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-08 11:41:16",
