            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經225指半日收報36863，上升83點或0.23%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日股早市逐步回穩，開報36863，升84點或0.23%，最高見36957，升178點或0.48%，中段向下，一度低見36606，跌173點或0.47%，其後回穩。</p>\n</div>",
