            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段偏軟，上證綜指以3331點開市，跌11點或0.34%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報10081點，亦跌22點或0.23%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌11點或0.29%，開報3820點；創業板指數開市報1994點，跌2點或0.12%。</p>\n</div>",
